{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T10:46:19.428Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "Feature Maps — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What Feature Maps Are"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "A "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "feature map"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is the output produced when a convolutional filter (kernel) processes an input image or a preceding layer in a CNN. It serves as the network's "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "internal representation"}, {"type": "text", "text": " of the data, highlighting specific patterns like edges, textures, or complex geometric shapes that the model has learned to recognize. Essentially, feature maps act as the \""}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "eyes"}, {"type": "text", "text": "\" of a CNN, transforming raw pixel values into meaningful abstractions."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each unique filter generates its own distinct feature map, highlighting where its particular pattern exists in the image."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why Feature Maps Matter in Generative AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Feature maps play crucial roles in CNNs for generative AI:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Role"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Impact"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Hierarchical feature extraction"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Enable CNNs to learn from simple edges to complex shapes across layers"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Spatial organization"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Provide structured, spatially-organized representation of learned features at various abstraction levels"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Object detection & generation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Power computer vision tasks like object detection, classification, and image generation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Efficient processing"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Allow CNNs to process large datasets faster by discarding unwanted data while retaining important information"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "In generative models like GANs, feature maps contain the internal representations that the network uses to understand and recreate realistic images."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How Feature Maps Are Created (Mathematical Foundation)"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The formula:"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mathematically, a feature map "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "F"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is generated by convolving an input image "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "I"}, {"type": "text", "text": " with a filter "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "W"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", followed by an activation function "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "σ"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "blockMath", "attrs": {"latex": "F = \\sigma(I * W + b)"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where:\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "I"}, {"type": "text", "text": " = input image\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "W"}, {"type": "text", "text": " = filter/kernel - "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "b"}, {"type": "text", "text": " = bias term\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "∗"}, {"type": "text", "text": " = convolution operation\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "σ"}, {"type": "text", "text": " = activation function (commonly ReLU)"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Creation process:"}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"start": 1, "type": null}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Filter sliding"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": A small matrix (kernel) slides across the entire input image"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Mathematical operation"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": The filter performs convolution with pixels it covers"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Value recording"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Result of each operation becomes a single pixel value in a new grid"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Grid formation"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": This new grid is the feature map"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Multiple filters"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Each unique filter creates its own distinct feature map"}]}]}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Input image → Convolution with filter → Activation function → Feature map"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each element of the feature map represents the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "activation of a specific feature"}, {"type": "text", "text": " within the image, capturing relevant spatial information learned during training."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Types of Feature Maps (Hierarchical Levels)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Feature maps evolve through hierarchical levels as data propagates through CNN layers:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Level"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What it detects"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Example"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Low-level"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (early layers)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Simple patterns"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Edges, lines, basic textures"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Mid-level"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (middle layers)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Combined patterns"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Corners, shapes, color gradients"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "High-level"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (deep layers)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Complex structures"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Objects, faces, complex geometric shapes"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Key principle"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": \"Generally, the deeper the layer, the more general/abstract the features extracted\"."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Characteristics"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "1. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Spatial correspondence"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each point in a feature map corresponds to a specific localized region in the original input image. This preserves spatial relationships."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "2. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Feature sharing"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "A feature map is passed through multiple layers; features found by previous layers propagate to each successive layer."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "3. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Multi-dimensional structure"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "2D feature map"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Single filter output (height × width)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "3D feature volume"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Multiple filters stacked (height × width × depth/channels)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "4. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Activation values"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Higher values = stronger presence of that feature at that location. The map shows \"where and how strongly certain features appear\"."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Benefits of Feature Maps"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Benefit"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Explanation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Automatic feature extraction"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "CNNs learn features adaptively without manual feature engineering"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Pattern detection"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Detect important features at multiple scales and locations"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Feature propagation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Previous layer features pass to successive layers for combination"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Decision support"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Capture essential features to aid network in decision-making"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Visualization"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Can be visualized to understand what input features the model detects"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Trade-offs & Limitations"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Limitation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Explanation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Information loss"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Pooling layers reduce feature map size, potentially losing fine-grained details"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Computational cost"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Deep networks with many feature maps require significant memory and computation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Interpretability"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "High-level feature maps can be difficult to interpret without visualization tools"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Fixed resolution"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Standard feature maps have fixed spatial dimensions; may struggle with variable-sized inputs"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Feature Maps in CNN Architecture (Typical Flow)"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Input Image (raw pixels)\n    ↓\nConvolutional Layer 1\n    ├─ Filter 1 → Feature Map 1 (vertical edges)\n    ├─ Filter 2 → Feature Map 2 (horizontal edges)\n    └─ Filter N → Feature Map N (textures)\n    ↓\nPooling Layer (downsamples all feature maps)\n    ↓\nConvolutional Layer 2\n    ├─ Combines low-level features → Mid-level features (corners, shapes)\n    └─ Creates new set of feature maps\n    ↓\nPooling Layer\n    ↓\nConvolutional Layer 3 (deep)\n    └─ Creates high-level feature maps (objects, faces)\n    ↓\nFully Connected Layer\n    ↓\nOutput (classification/generation)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each convolutional layer produces multiple feature maps (one per filter)."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mental Model"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Think of feature maps as "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "different security cameras"}, {"type": "text", "text": " watching a building:"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Camera 1"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Filter 1) detects only vertical motion → creates feature map showing vertical edges"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Camera 2"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Filter 2) detects only horizontal motion → creates feature map showing horizontal edges"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Camera 3"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Filter 3) detects color changes → creates feature map showing textures"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each camera records where its specific pattern appears in the building"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Together, all cameras provide a complete picture of what's happening"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Or think of feature maps as "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "layers of a detective's analysis"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Layer 1"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": \"I see lines here\" (edges)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Layer 2"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": \"Those lines form corners\" (shapes)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Layer 3"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": \"Those corners form a face\" (objects)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each layer builds on the previous, creating increasingly abstract understanding"}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Visualization & Analysis"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Feature maps can be visualized to understand what the CNN detects:"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# Example: Visualizing feature maps\nfeature_maps = model.predict(image)\nfor i in range(len(feature_maps)):\n    plt.imshow(feature_maps[:, :, i])\n    plt.title(f\"Feature Map {i}\")"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Purpose"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": \"To understand what features from the input are detected or retained by the model\"."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Best practice"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Visualize feature maps at different depths to see how features evolve from detailed to abstract."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Feature Maps vs. Related Concepts"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Concept"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Difference"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Input image"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Raw pixels; feature map = processed representation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Filter/kernel"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The learnable weights; feature map = output after applying filter"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Activation map"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Same as feature map (synonymous terms)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Layer output"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Feature map is the specific output of convolutional layers"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Takeaways"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Feature maps are "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "outputs of convolutional layers"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that represent where specific features appear in the input"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each filter generates its own "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "distinct feature map"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", creating multiple maps per layer"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Feature maps evolve "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "hierarchically"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": early layers detect edges; deeper layers detect complex objects"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "They provide "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "spatially organized representations"}, {"type": "text", "text": " preserving where features occur"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Feature maps enable "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "automatic feature extraction"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", eliminating manual feature engineering"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "In generative AI, feature maps are the CNN's "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "internal \"perception\""}, {"type": "text", "text": " used to understand and generate images"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Higher activation values indicate "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "stronger feature presence"}, {"type": "text", "text": " at that location"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Feature maps are fundamental to how CNNs \"see\" and understand visual data, making them essential for computer vision tasks in generative AI including image generation, object detection, and style transfer."}]}]}}